+++ __**Determination:**__

* SCP-5578 demonstrates limited capacity for sapience as outlined in Pseudohuman Civil Rights Act Polity Statute;
* SCP-5578 does not meet all criteria for "autonomous" as outlined in Pseudohuman Civil Rights Act Polity Statute
+++ __**Recommendation:**__

* The Committee determines that SCP-5578 may be eligible for **##green|Partial Exemption##** under the Reintegration Protocol, pending decisions regarding "autonomous" legal definition. Provide SCP-5578 with adequate social engagement and maintenance to preserve function until deliberations are complete.

@@ @@
